profile:
We are uniquely equipped with the machinery necessary for on-site cutting of steel roofing panels. This provides us with a unque competitive advantage and opportunity for customers and other roofing contractors! When installing a steel roof on your home, contractors take measurements and order custom sized panels to fit your unique roof, and then install those panels accordingly. The cutting and wait time for these custom materials can cause delays in the installation of your new roof. A delay in starting work is dissatisfying for both contractors and customers alike and we can change that! 

By providing the services of steel cutting, we can order the raw materials to be delivered to the worksite and cut the custom panels on-site. The result is a more immediate start time, less waste from inaccurate measures, and very happy customers.
services:
On-Site Steel Roof Cutting,
Roof Installation, Siding Installation, Soffit & Fascia Installation,
Standing Seam Steel Roofing

profile:
We serve Barrie and surrounding area, from the Greater Toronto Area to Huntsville, and are known for our affordable prices and commitment to performing quality work. Whether a huge storm ruined the roof on your home or your roof could use a few new shingles, we can help you out. We take pride in the fact that no job is too large or small for us to handle and will take care of your entire roof replacement or repair job with excellence from start to finish.

With more than 50 years of combined experience in the roofing industry, we are confident that you will benefit from allowing us handle all of your roofing needs. Sorry, we do not do metal roofs or flat roofing. One of the main things that sets us apart from other roofing companies is the fact that we only do one job at a time. This allows us to make sure that each job is done properly and that we do not run into delays along the way.
services:
Roof Repairs—If your roof is leaking or sustained significant damage in a storm, we can help. We will do everything we can to get your roof fixed quickly and affordably.
Roof Replacements—The roof on your home wasn’t designed to last forever. If it’s time to replace your roof, we can take care of the entire replacement process from start to finish.
Roof Installations—During the construction of a new home, it’s essential that the roof on the property is installed correctly. Thanks to our experience in the roofing industry, you can rest assured that we will install your new roof properly.
